<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFBrowning1993">Browning, Jackson (1993). Jack A. Gottschalk. ed (PDF). <i><a href="http://www.bhopal.com/pdfs/browning.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.bhopal.com/pdfs/browning.pdf" rel="nofollow">Union Carbide: Disaster at Bhopal</a></i>. Crisis Response: Inside Stories on Managing Image Under Siege. Detroit<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.bhopal.com/pdfs/browning.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.bhopal.com/pdfs/browning.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.bhopal.com/pdfs/browning.pdf</a></span>.  "Union Carbide's former vice-president of health, safety and environmental programs tells how he dealt with the catastrophe from a PR point of view."</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Union+Carbide%3A+Disaster+at+Bhopal&amp;rft.aulast=Browning&amp;rft.aufirst=Jackson&amp;rft.au=Browning%2C+Jackson&amp;rft.date=1993&amp;rft.series=Crisis+Response%3A+Inside+Stories+on+Managing+Image+Under+Siege&amp;rft.place=Detroit&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhopal.com%2Fpdfs%2Fbrowning.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Bhopal_disaster"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
