<h4><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Bhopal_disaster&amp;action=edit&amp;section=43" title="Edit section: Contamination of site">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Contamination of site</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book"><i>A Report on Mercury Contamination of Groundwater near the Union Carbide Factory at Bhopal</i>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=A+Report+on+Mercury+Contamination+of+Groundwater+near+the+Union+Carbide+Factory+at+Bhopal&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Bhopal_disaster"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> Peoples' Science Institute, Dehra Doon (2001)</li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book"><i>Foul Debris. The UCIL plant is still a health hazard</i>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Foul+Debris.+The+UCIL+plant+is+still+a+health+hazard&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Bhopal_disaster"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> Down to Earth, Dec 15 (2003).</li>
</ul>
<p><a name="Mixed" id="Mixed"></a></p>
<h4><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Bhopal_disaster&amp;action=edit&amp;section=44" title="Edit section: Mixed">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Mixed</span></h4>
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.american.edu/ted/bhopal.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.american.edu/ted/bhopal.htm" rel="nofollow">"Bhopal Disaster"</a>. Trade Environmental Database. TED case studies no. 233, American University, Washington (1 Nov 1997)<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.american.edu/ted/bhopal.htm" class="external free" title="http://www.american.edu/ted/bhopal.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.american.edu/ted/bhopal.htm</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Bhopal+Disaster&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.pub=Trade+Environmental+Database.+TED+case+studies+no.+233%2C+American+University%2C+Washington+%281+Nov+1997%29&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.american.edu%2Fted%2Fbhopal.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Bhopal_disaster"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://bioterrorism.slu.edu/pulmonary/quick/methyliso.pdf" class="external text" title="http://bioterrorism.slu.edu/pulmonary/quick/methyliso.pdf" rel="nofollow">"Chemical Terrorism Fact Sheet: Methyl Isocyanate."</a> (PDF)<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://bioterrorism.slu.edu/pulmonary/quick/methyliso.pdf" class="external free" title="http://bioterrorism.slu.edu/pulmonary/quick/methyliso.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://bioterrorism.slu.edu/pulmonary/quick/methyliso.pdf</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Chemical+Terrorism+Fact+Sheet%3A+Methyl+Isocyanate.&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbioterrorism.slu.edu%2Fpulmonary%2Fquick%2Fmethyliso.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Bhopal_disaster"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> CSB&amp;EI, Saint Louis University School of Public Health, USA</li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book"><i>The Trade Union Report on Bhopal</i>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Trade+Union+Report+on+Bhopal&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Bhopal_disaster"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> ICFTU-ICEF, Geneva, Switzerland (1985) See <a href="http://bhopal.bard.edu/resources/research.php" class="external text" title="http://bhopal.bard.edu/resources/research.php" rel="nofollow">The Bhopal Memory Project</a></li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.bhopal.net/oldsite/unproventechnology.html" class="external text" title="http://www.bhopal.net/oldsite/unproventechnology.html" rel="nofollow">"Unproven technology"</a>. Bhopal.net (14 Nov 2002)<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.bhopal.net/oldsite/unproventechnology.html" class="external free" title="http://www.bhopal.net/oldsite/unproventechnology.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.bhopal.net/oldsite/unproventechnology.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Unproven+technology&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.pub=Bhopal.net+%2814+Nov+2002%29&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhopal.net%2Foldsite%2Funproventechnology.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Bhopal_disaster"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
